# Cross-origin isolation so the wasm image codecs (oxipng, etc.) can run
# multi-threaded via SharedArrayBuffer. `credentialless` keeps cross-origin
# subresources (Google Fonts, Iconify) working; browsers without it (Safari)
# simply fall back to the single-threaded codecs.
/*
  Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin
  Cross-Origin-Embedder-Policy: credentialless
  Origin-Agent-Cluster: ?1
